ETHICAL USE ADDENDUM
──────────────────────────────────────────────

While this software is open source under the MIT License, users are strongly
encouraged to follow ethical guidelines when using voice cloning technology:

RECOMMENDED PRACTICES:
• Obtain explicit consent before cloning any person's voice
• Clearly disclose when synthetic voices are being used
• Respect privacy and data protection laws
• Use the technology responsibly and transparently

DISCOURAGED USES:
• Impersonation without consent
• Fraud, deception, or identity theft
• Non-consensual deepfakes
• Any illegal activities

Users bear full responsibility for ensuring their use complies with applicable
laws and ethical standards.

